data.revised_prompt: A detailed image of an isolated stop sign. The sign is set against a completely empty background, emphasizing its loneliness. The sign itself radiates a vivid red colour, with the word 'STOP' clearly inscribed in bold, white letters. The pole of the stop sign is metallic grey, slightly weathered revealing the harsh reality of time. This lone sentinel stands strong, despite the harsh weather conditions or the absence of any viewer.

message.content: The image features a red octagonal stop sign prominently displayed. The word "STOP" is written in bold white letters across the center of the sign. The background is a soft, neutral gradient, which emphasizes the sign itself. The sign is mounted on a metallic pole, and the overall lighting enhances its visibility and draws attention to its important message.
